DESCRIPTION:
Enjoy the beauty of a BreezeArt® Premium Flag
Designer artwork is permanently dyed for more vivid, fade-resistant color. Our exclusive SolarSilk® polyester is heavier for greater outdoor durability, yet has a softer, silkier feel for better drape and movement in the breeze.


SolarSilk® vs Two-Sided Fabric
See the BreezeArt Difference

Many of our competitors champion their two-sided flags. While this is an interesting feature, it comes at a cost – the beauty and brightness of the flag is compromised. Two-sided printing requires fabric with a “blackout” layer between the front and back of the flag, dulling colors and blocking light.

The way we see it, color trumps all. Instead of opting for fabric that allows two-sided printing, we chose our exclusive SolarSilk fabric because it best represents the beauty and brightness of our artists’ work. It’s amazing to see how the sun enhances the vibrant colors in our BreezeArt® flags. Why get in nature’s way?

Buy BreezeArt. Buy the Best.
